comments: If initial two 1's are omitted, denominator of y coordinate of (2n+1)*P where P is generator for rational points on curve y^2+y = x^3-x.
references: B. Mazur, Arithmetic on curves, Bull. Amer Math. Soc. 14 (1986), 207-259; see p 225.
